name: Layer Texture and Tone BatCat Attacks

metadata.name: I met the BatCat on a dark road.
metadata.description:
I met the BatCat on a dark road.

The BatCat is an ancient demon. This demon changes the textures of objects and creatures. It merges creatures together in grotesque ways. It will radiate your skeleton. If you see a strange creature in a strange place, you've seen what the demon can do. It made BunnyFace. BunnyFace is too nice for this sick world. BunnyFace runs.
